data.description: Welcome to your dream home !  Built in 2018, this 3 bed 2 bath gem boasts a 2 car garage on a spacious .45 acre lot.  Enjoy a stylish all white kitchen with upgraded quartz countertops, built in entertainment center, coffee bar and chic wine rack.  Exterior features a 6 ft vinyl privacy fence and a refreshing saltwater pool added in 2023.  As a Millstone South resident you will have access to the clubhouse, tennis courts, a gym and community pool.  Your perfect home awaits !!
